Validate
========

### Dependencies

- PHP 5.3+

### Usage

```php
<?php
  
  $test = lib\validate::test(
    array(
      'name'  => 'John',
      'nick'  => 'JohnnyBoy',
      'email' => 'john.doe@gmail.com'
    ),
    array(
      'name'  => 'required | between(2,20) | alpha, message: please specify a name',
      'nick'  => 'between(1,20) | alphanumeric',
      'email' => 'required | email, message: invalid email address'
    )
  );
  
?>
```